(10032, 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/l_2_oHMP83nGDYBNMTK-7qXGHF8iiYbo9C-kODesK5r4PmlIqKRruqQtlUgyg7DVVpev=s180-rw', 'The Ants: Underground Kingdom', 'Seven City', 'Strategy', 'In The Ants: Underground Kingdom, you are the ultimate Ant Ruler to lead your Queen and build your Anthill.\n\nTo survive and reproduce, wars between animals take place frequently in nature. In The Ants: Underground Kingdom, you are the ultimate Ant Ruler to build the Anthill, lead the Queen, grow the colony, and defend against enemies. For the glory and prosperity of your ant empire, you must show your own strategies resourcefulness.\n \n--Game Features‚Äî\n\n„ÄêBuild Anthill„Äë\nThe Anthill of an ant colony is the same as the castle of an empire, which provides a safe place for the offspring to grow. Anthill layout is strategically crucial, so you should plan your hive wisely, construct tunnels, thus building your ideal ant empire!\n\n„ÄêHatch Ants„Äë\nThe number of ants represents the rise and fall of an ant empire. For the development of your ant empire, you must hatch as many ants as possible. Lead them to fight, plunder resources, and expand your territory!\n\n„ÄêMutate Ants„Äë\nTo plunder resources and expand territory, you must build a mighty Ant Troop. In addition to numerous advanced Soldier Ants, You also need to have leaders for your Ant Troops: The Special Ants. You can get powerful Special Ants by hatching mutant eggs. Your Ant Troop will gain a sweeping victory with a proper combination of Soldier Ants and Special Ants.\n\n„ÄêCreate Alliance„Äë\nFighting alone will never be easy. Success only leaves for the alliances who think alike. By creating or joining an Alliance, you can help each other to grow and fight together. With the help of allies, the ant empire under your command will surely take its place in this Ant Kingdom!\n\nThe Ants: Underground Kingdom provides an instant online customer service, which will surely give you a better gaming experience.\nNo matter what kind of questions you have, we are here to help as much as possible. You can contact us through the following channels:\n\nOfficial LINE: @planetant (don\'t forget \"@\")\nOfficial Discord: https://discord.gg/PazRBH8kCC\nOfficial Email: theantsgame@gmail.com\nOfficial Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TheAntsGame\n\nAttention!\nThe Ants: Underground Kingdom is free to download. However, some items in the game are not free. Players must be at least 3 years old to download it, as defined in the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. Besides, devices should have access to network as this is an online game.', 4.1, 8985, '0000-00-00', 1000000, '[\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/vbkR3ojb9I_qEC51yjIB9CkDwReNYTe-AfTFPLtVqtz8T2f7q7l9JxEr6rGK579yGnc=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/Y6M_GzB8UL0qjkUo8FIdqkptjM1eD6H5AXdd_YimeuWkBF77LFmuSKdi2SSK3uOq8GY=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/E2y9fIYCXyzxqyoEDfgyR_1mEQT99YJ6JZJawumwoa7-g4878kaSuKpRO4XK4d69BJo=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/IXiHOARzBWs5J0MdCXSY-pW4FeXouK6EgYed0U9SiDSQ0UU5VmcVcX0ts5r-Ie_Z2xE=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/i7dhzeI1bmNBjFkMzfmusov8sARONOt3nY-poybgd5z1fUnFbKytRZlaOHWLKQZSWCq7=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/yacBeLbFQhvheATw2g2mr9Qch7_xKddx6OkXUGafn03CZjqc61CaPSY1GY2fOc0nKPY=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/i9YI_ncIzcFEf3KynKXMfLHBpCuuwpTgTEkojDT0qZM-ZU-xlHIAXV0P_qCPyEDbmg=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/3ORZnW5XYD5wFBDYoDUdt7a_UMeXoUss_x_96x3wxkptp1qt8x5xdb2SiW6n1S1Kcpc=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/V5hUl3tmZt6MrHumzo7qMYygV1sPPzXrl8LVAVgAyaZNhCBKe2rBuGp97UK6G6sYkkw=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/1nQaEOVp6TYAGYZAsL6Eo8dD7AVrcQZgKff0nyT5pvNajo0mIYRzV5r0mxpWK917_mJy=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/SNa4exx-YcnPDGKMKbHDtoIIUqMCKaCoYqWJp8W1ZcjUvQpKF5c8wp0s4RBZWrszKQ=w720-