ou were born as a ninja!\n\n\n\n\n\nThe tense atmosphere is created with the help of upbeat music, realistic \"broken vase\" sounds, and game design in the style of \"Mama, I\'m a criminal\". Besides, you\'ll never know what\'s waiting for you on the next level‚Ä¶\n\n\n\nFirst of all, the big boss is a target that\'s not so easy to kill üí£. Be patient and make several attempts! Second, collect as much money as you can (actually, this is just good practical advice). Third, enemies in the game can be easily eliminated with a one shot. Don\'t waste your precious time on other parts of their bodies! And last but not least: be a good person and only fight the bad guys!\n\n‚òõ Psssst! Listen to me‚Ä¶ Some of your friends are already on their way to becoming a ninja! What are you waiting for? Download the game and start your bloody mission!', 4.2, 108639, '0000-00-00', 10000000, '[\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/k54uAhcFgIPM06K7Uvq3GKAGX6cllhT081bkpKMqDVaAVy3zh-F38qGPlTz_czv7t9A=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/Mg_QAMlXUPmtKmegIx6RBB4_GFHcwNz6J27Ncuvkd--2LIyxl4jaOh1cm_O0ByunE4Y=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/Ikl0NPtHhZz8IBNa-FWf2bFHYZsB_v_ki9WDPxBPtfjpq_nY_peMDyUIlOU3YJj2N-o=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/mPLqfG9d2Q9H-0mds3UY1yGeAtlbE7CNYk2wV1C07ppkMAjNgcWpQq0F4T1oRQooGMB9=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/2ZNy1H1yWBOxRmIohuQNXnidpWeeLxxI1WzIdCi7WRbBW1ypt6znBGo-6b_R2e_muYL6=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/FWbspU6wP4lMhjznZD0jhxVoKbNTKYjjv7SsO6Btftd4pWNjWgsmuTjOxdBYy_9ppWPE=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/EqY32O73tkpHeSGx3_gsFswkRtiWKLw-pFT_DHF0_u2m8t-fIns-DbaU_OLml8UxtX4g=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/hnrOp38rC9c-H0azaogCufads3jEJv4UftEWhDhFgcHzSFj7bRid0LKCucNZ5MylwJxw=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/53AwmlCfHiS5jupwswH6oAQcJEuuEPLhXs-ru8FvqKceQSnVw5MFTTTT7J_FGQ28GA=w720-h3