(10168, 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/4r0_YyQgXNUQOzdf1Wi0DUfAG8f1aC_xiBw024RgxhI3uR2Eed5NJZtyMP8h-_I1hOk7=s180-rw', 'Solitaire TriPeaks: Play Free Solitaire Card Games', 'GSN Games, Inc.', 'Card', 'Cards. They‚Äôve been around for literally centuries. They have long-lasting appeal.\n\nSolitaire. Countless hours have passed while people have entertained themselves by playing solitaire. If boredom was as life-threatening as children proclaim, solitaire would have saved tens, possibly hundreds, of millions of lives. No joke.\n\nTriPeaks. Arguably the most fun Solitaire game of them all.\n\nSolitaire TriPeaks. No doubt about it - *the* most fun TriPeaks version out there. It‚Äôs a little bit Golf, it‚Äôs a little bit Pyramid, and it‚Äôs a whole lot of depth. It‚Äôs a deep game, my friend. A very deep game.\n\nHere‚Äôs the deal. You‚Äôve got the basics - the game itself. Then you throw in things like unique Hazards and Boosters, Wild Cards, a whole slew of tableau setups, and you‚Äôre just skimming the surface. You keep on playing, and then you‚Äôll discover whole new worlds - tons of levels, Clubs, leagues, the ability to chat with your Club Members, a Friend Center, and events that will challenge your mind, and satisfy your soul. We don‚Äôt play the hyperbole game. We state the facts.\n\nOh, and lest we forget, this game is like being on a vacation with a cast of some crazy characters you‚Äôll likely fall in love with pretty quick. There are the two hosts to the game, Tiki and Poi. Tiki‚Äôs a Tiki - nobody really knows what the heck he is, and that‚Äôs just how it is. And Poi? He‚Äôs his adorable dog and sidekick. Together, they‚Äôll make you laugh and keep you inspired to take on the next level. Then there are other characters as you move through the game, like Pele, the Volcano Goddess. Don‚Äôt mess with her. And Marina, she‚Äôs as sweet as sweet can be. There are penguins, bunnies, monkeys, a parrot and a curmudgeonly old Pirate named Captain Karma.\n\nAlso, there‚Äôs the art. You won‚Äôt believe the art in these levels - it‚Äôs like out of this world, my friend. Every level provides an enticing background. Some make you want to take a vacation on the beach. Others make you want to fly in space, or delve the deepest depths of the ocean.\n\nThere you have it. Download this one game today, and you won‚Äôt be searching the app store for much anymore.\n\nPrivacy Policy:\nhttp://gsngamesnetwork.com/privacy.html', 4.5, 649567, '0000-00-00', 10000000, '[\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/Bx5ezG4l6UQPbRd0D9F3Mntk5G2JUQ9ZF4zJFYalCk1BVCN4nk0IOEeRRIpW9pRxFVE=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/_Ua4EM5byE2TOXs9I_vrEi5s7HAxohJwJMGrGKSRjnRgQ3wATd1FeJs-zNMsXHqbmYM=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/tlhN3NiBtVMmhaOC1VSuFHooRDuywaO7iUyn757JZYs9AIgruoYg1NWDbtyMnZX4SVg=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/kTddno0GP5dADPQlh6FDd7tT-hsb5yP7LDTrf0e-vhdVzTnFva0h9cMVTaK8GRna8g=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/gSgmHSgJO3WGdFgBduLjP26Nzzb39EdT19zAksxk88Ri5XzSk3XLIAAOMuQTWqaUw5lK=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/FPvrmge_BveZXDE1BlE3V6JuAbkgZbVrJ2u46VFeyKo77GFwOdg8nVmePvVqK04l_2Mi=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/2jZ8D9vIBnRsOPxXo9H7liExYeyIgh3O9gEz4dSyhl6kexxQavwpYuitSzR7PeyoihU=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/HkUzCi4eh9Jhx4sD_a2vl8kiWY0K2bTr1-3q-FjQeTj-Lyoa8jA79tam_cXbOTyvWq8=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/xvedrm44cToy59576o9XGBU4MJGojbRxZ1bo-BxNg2qBdHRqkeNJ96AAK1dMhWU3vpo=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/_RDng96Bem-TkJY7ORD4pn3QP3awnfUaVdjFuEZqMFDJUne3M46kcErLuRqPwXHheA=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/Czj1hHAUkcX-PQ7uH8NGSUtmxfj9H88lB060IFtl7xH-rIUnS8xNE1X_SUZjUob8aTA=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/v66MNIIxIib5XPvUFzBel5U1osx4NHm8M1PgpbAuDkzRAF4_j5Q5R9meHo-NRoH2-g=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://pl