(10226, 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/4k9adsl5lch3UPvmPuGIlupIGmz8mSroVk_viKsaBOMqFZMC6brXANNsw7qXhP1Mfho=s180-rw', 'Hill Climb Racing 2', 'Fingersoft', 'Racing', 'From the Creators of the Original Hill Climb Racing Comes Hill Climb Racing 2! It\'s Bigger, It\'s Better And It\'s Much Much Funner!?\n\nHill Climb Racing 2 is a free to play online multiplayer racing game with dozens of tracks, cars and character customization at your fingertips.\n\n\n\nüöó\n\nDrive your way through the trophy road to earn new medals from cups and unlock the ability to purchase new cars, bikes, trucks and even an epic tank with your hard earned coins received from racing. With over 20+ vehicles to unlock, pick the one that climbs you to the pole position!\n\nüîß\n\nPurchase upgrades with coins won from car racing and use them to improve your ride. With over 16 unlockable parts to choose from, combine and collect these parts to improve your performance! Mix the upgrades in unique ways to maximize your driving capabilities and race to the top!\n\nüé©\n\nEarn and unlock a variety of customization options for both your character and also your garage of vehicles! Look cool while racing and tailor your character to your own unique style! There are thousands of combinations! Then take it to the next level up and customize your car with different skins and tires to make your racer truly unique!\n\nüèÅ\n\nThe popular adventure mode from Hill Climb Racing 1 also makes it‚Äôs return in this sequel! See how far you can drive in this endless race mode! Earn coins to upgrade your vehicles and help you with the online cup‚Äôs mode and multiplayer team events!\n\nüë®‚Äçüë©‚Äçüë¶‚Äçüë¶\n\nTake part in online races with your friends. Create or join a multiplayer race team and see how high in the leaderboard you can reach! With online multiplayer leaderboards and events that change weekly there‚Äôs a host of activities to take part in! And as an added bonus a weekly multiplayer team chest to unlock, so there‚Äôs plenty of incentive to make your dream team and play online with your friends!\n\nüïπ\n\nPerform Stunts, flips and wheelies or crash your car trying! With our unique physics based car simulation you can pull off daring stunts that other car games can‚Äôt compete with! Performing stunts can help you boost your performance and unlock even more coins for you to spend on upgrades!\n\nüèÜ\n\nIn Cup‚Äôs mode you drive against 3 other online players. Battle it out and race to the finish line in the quickest time possible! The Cup‚Äôs mode will have you driving and competing in multiplayer games with hundreds of different levels in a variety of terrains. From driving through the scenic Countryside to the dangerous Frostfire Caverns!\n\nRemember that we\'re always reading your feedback and are hard at work creating new original content for our car games: new cars, bikes, cups, levels and features for Hill Climb Racing 1 & 2. If you find a bug or have a crash let us know so we can fix it. We really appreciate it if you\'d report what you like or dislike and any issues you may have with our driving games to support@fingersoft.com, please include your device make and model.\n\nFollow Us: üîç\n* Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Fingersoft\n* Twitter: https://twitter.com/HCR_Official_\n* Website: https://www.fingersoft.com\n* Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hillclimbracing_official\n* Discord: https://discord.com/invite/fingersoft\n\nTerms of Use: https://fingersoft.com/eula-web/\nPrivacy Policy: https://fingersoft.com/privacy-policy/\n\nHill Climb Racing‚Ñ¢Ô∏è is a registered trademark of Fingersoft Ltd. All rights reserved.', 4.3, 4083514, '0000-00-00', 100000000, '[\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/bJbzJzp97R44-BcnNtp7JTHdNQGx19aYJPiDVkmehqkuzeHNfThyifDBs5nd9ahzqmg=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/TkGRKa3GDAyQybZOL9HVfXPseuZCooojuIBUez-1eLGZR-WfhcyXdDWO2jw1coIsTQ0=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleuserconten