(10243, 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/BWXMOiyHGAq5iWuCzfTfWOH7-9lHpTIfbyKtVmXbxcksfXrKOwztjz1KWoUJpccoaw=s180-rw', 'Johnny Trigger - Action Shooting Game', 'SayGames', 'Action', 'Johnny Trigger ‚Äì International Man of Mayhem!\n\nStylish, deadly and smooth as a billiard ball, Johnny Trigger is a man on a mission in this non-stop platform shooter game where the action never ends.\n\nDo you have what it takes to bring down the underground world of the mafia? ‚ÄúLess talk, more bullets‚Äù ‚Äì that‚Äôs Johnny‚Äôs motto as he runs, jumps, spins, slides and keeps on shooting till every bad guy‚Äôs bitten the dust.\n\nüî• üî•\n\n‚öà Thousands of levels of murderous mayhem to fight through, each demanding a unique tactical solution and speedy trigger fingers! Johnny never stops moving, so when the bad guys line up in your sights, you‚Äôve got just once chance to get shooting.\n\n‚öà Be careful not to hit hostages, though. After all you‚Äôre the hero of this game, not some crazed killer! Should you accidentally end the life of an innocent civilian, it‚Äôs back to square one.\n\n‚öà Hit those hard-to-reach scumbags with the power of physics! Trick shots, ricochets, explosions and gravity are all part of Johnny‚Äôs crime-fighting arsenal‚Ä¶\n\n‚öà ...along with guns galore! Cause serious havoc with 57 unique weapons to collect ‚Äì 11 pistols, 12 SMGs, 9 automatic rifles, 10 superguns üî´ and 4 Ultimate guns with fearsome capabilities guaranteed to give the bad guys a nasty shock. For the completist, there‚Äôs also 5 base guns, 3 bundle guns and 3 VIP guns. Basically, a shedload of guns to collect, cherish and slaughter gangsters with.\n\n‚öà On the subject of sheds, collect keys to unlock Johnny‚Äôs 10 awesome base rooms and get hammering to turn them into luxurious hideaways. Turns out our action hero‚Äôs quite the handyman in his free time.\n\n‚öà Sweet graphics and a banging soundtrack ‚Äì Johnny‚Äôs world would be a great place to chill if it weren‚Äôt for all those pesky gangsters lurking round every corner. Just think how nice it‚Äôll be once you‚Äôve massacred every last one of them!\n\n‚öà More than 20 different stylish skins to help Johnny go undercover in the murky underworld of organized crime, and then blast the living hell out of it!\n\n‚öà Boss battles demand all of Johnny‚Äôs wits and sharp shooting as you take down the lords of the underworld in a leaping, spinning storm of bullets.\n\nüí£ üí£\n\nDive straight in and get shooting! Johnny Trigger‚Äôs short but immensely satisfying levels make it the perfect action game to fill a short break between meetings, lectures or lessons. And if you‚Äôve got a little more time, there‚Äôs so much to collect and a new challenge round every corner.', 4.4, 1446540, '0000-00-00', 100000000, '[\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/R7_vETUmN7RwKf4v0eaE_46lvMVkl9xGci83_9jrRdoDdvRNZGjT-FpCQfh7VxJZ_fvk=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/v38ORtyUKEITBbMFn4AJfQW4R0V-LFVFzyhqv78GNXI5bTSb2BCHTK4L96Ogq9VSABE=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/81Y86AXAxPZ2CtsrTRado2hRMDaqu5NICT0Kif-tEUHDe1mGXBecyB4HCQ9OqjVt8g=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/Of0jlWAgMw1LVp52YOqfYOoc39eZ4VN8hSbPl5kwnoDmu8XSZFdofP_cX5S6uRR0vJs=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/cADjGrx7STear-zUxVegkDyDULag0f-hPey16H60CLdmX-F_E4VWPv8DN1a7F9UTSPY=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/4D5ga37vdl07G2lqiE5Xyx-Yry1Xr4R43VVSuU-EE8PDkhd7_FLwWkxj_b-t-2EHTWWS=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/qVRxN8WyUna_EolNhD2ABm49A_bbGOPPcTF6XHRG9q_WydiX5F0ZR-Y4QC0qzN7wow=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/ezOnVNqYEH9xVF62rKotkGInxmAcKYsDzEo9yDdjTLGOEAa39mmHMVzlOSG-KytF9QVG=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/ptc_2gENUx-YTB3S9XOQEgHXLlSukrUKjQfUndDQQm0o6E0MzR-O-FMbOFbvt12JvtV2=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/dFpL6_0quyUY0gt78qhFfS-cD94pOmCMXAfauGs-btrkMg