(10311, 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/OFnrs8go_NIO5sAQGzDu572maaWRTkxu-hKCiHdpgcLLPS3GOcuZ_aISzuVvO2_SrVE=s180-rw', 'Piano Fire - EDM Music & New Rhythm', 'Adaric Music', 'Music', '5,000,000+ players around the world have chosen us! Play Piano Fire on mobile anywhere today!\n\nPiano Fire is a special game in different genres of piano games with wonderful gameplay. Blends piano and EDM music perfectly, you can feel the collision of ice and fire, get addicted to hot and popular songs around the world!\n\nHow to Play:\nIt‚Äôs similar to other piano games, tap the tiles continuously to follow the music melody and don\'t miss any tile. Prove how fast and accurate you can play!\n\nGame features:\n- Real music feeling when tapping the tiles.\n- More albums and songs of various styles.\n- Cool design and graphics.\n- Easy to play, hard to master. Tapping only the music tile in some high-speed songs can be a real challenge!\n\nDo not hesitate to try Piano Fire online and offline! This excellent piano game has more surprises in store for you than you can imagine!', 4.6, 77741, '0000-00-00', 10000000, '[\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/seQY1cy-mRwW3Kf9aajeb-9bg-AEC7HJFu6_A0y1p_VtZfAwk-_UI2XhuXXUBYeAYkOg=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/-kwQm2GTDpaSk5J8VRWhtL6CLOB0Rnrt5_ccjZQVhOcu66PWnEDQks-iV4dR-u17PA=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/h_bFtHekwsoT19xxc3ysQRxFlpU1tNL_v5w8hf5lP0FpGbY8etT-roTp46kQKlELxQ=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/hfmRQXt4j2E9iXbqKw--gtj9FFWa1Ve3VNNefMRgROA7ahV1vJk1sK7u0EBobzCZq6G1=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/EVf-wsIyOrdhikXaXtDh847k6seUCLTlbmV3cLUmITAVzJ-L_c0h8mYhWO481Byv9gu1=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/7zevRJN8LmrXJJeB45Ash2R4zpoW9fhR9G2PtI2SSZNQq2nbbGtuaurXe5V89lY1Qbdd=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/Nr8INxvBQ7gfquUd3t7e5m7XSaRRH9SWnjVA8Lr7GtSooa5kDkMLI4IVBlNlryeqEoy4=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://