ew, deeper layer to the story depicted in the drawing. Only you can make the invisible üîç visible!\n\n‚òÖ Enjoy the delightful graphics with their unique cartoon style and cute animations.\n\n‚òÖ Provides hours of fun for teens, seniors, and anyone in between who wants to keep their brain sharp!\n\n‚òÖ The optional music, sound effects, and vibration settings give you more control over your gameplay experience.\n\nStrengthen your reasoning skills and put your mind to the test with a relaxing and amusing thinking game. The best part is that there is no way to mess up or fail: if you erase the wrong thing, the picture will just reset! The point is to make you think, not make you cry! üò≠\n\nBut you‚Äôll still have to think outside the box to master this brain game! Who knew solving logic puzzles could be so enjoyable and satisfying?!', 4, 378839, '0000-00-00', 50000000, '[\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/O7OomsXkBq7T_Cq-cYQ96TS_2K7vbr-zGfcOtBV6UmRlTNMQym8WVZgyFcsxsC1wsw=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/gEbpG-Qjl6-zvi7JL2Hz6YpyLZ_K7IVALTBmX9aOxKRwZdLP_67yza_Q1FyASevaxDM=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/VjlenYiVFBE4xMKvv7KHpvh-B3nR-tMPsvOhuyyEWYDzx6scH3LiVrSHBMn9gx81QhRo=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/ZNre3jJH89bxFWg_jbDBUieZd2bRI607tc-nfIUJJyF03hVSg6-Au2xXhgshQuJvOw=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/tCp0AkL38XrORKFbKwzwblqiBAFwBvUVOQnmjJWq_JTG7XZFQLq1DMYQGMp9lxq9vcE=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/3FaLFNK2qOE4rVIfec4_4ZI8GhgqnG4RVSxKWVrzfVvtXP8oPpTmdbVUqAONFQmqrYc=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/forAPVviBKtaMzWFM6Xoa-VaGEtGA_PhAAHVO4fvgVO93OhgBtVh_24VAVQ0EHJZZw=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/E6cL5LKhPpoj0fqwy99P_1cxIHKABvqa7-U3aiyiPSV2OiCg-_P6WiURc6dEk8_7lA=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/JU3XEMSwvhYjIttq36TK0g-pKLTkN7UHLafQKiEGZhGzmed-G4I2PEsrfyGN3KbPF_vN=w720-h310-rw\", 