r RPG locations spread over a sprawling, fully-voiced story campaign.\n\n\nMMORPG games shouldn‚Äôt be a slog! Autoplay levels to spend less time grinding and more time exploring.\n\n\n\n* Items are available for purchase in this MMORPG gacha game. Some paid items may not be refundable depending on the type of item.\n* RAID: Shadow Legends is available in English, Russian, German, French, Spanish, Italian, Ukrainian, Chinese Traditional, Chinese Simplified, Korean, Turkish, Japanese, and Portuguese. We understand that role-playing is always more immersive in your native language!\n\nRAID Official Website: https://plarium.com/\nRAID Support: raid.support@plarium.com\nOur RPG Community: https://plarium.com/forum/en/raid-shadow-legends/\nPrivacy Policy: https://plarium.com/en/legal/privacy-and-cookie-policy/\nTerms of Use: https://plarium.com/en/legal/terms-of-use/\nCCPA Employee and Applicant Notice: https://plarium.com/en/legal/ccpa/', 4.2, 1346487, '0000-00-00', 10000000, '[\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/0AJh4CnUwZEHHO6pURpxUgdzQpiQqDVHOp3WW7Bk0u2-BgrzaHYldA6UZAIhKpxMNA=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/3TtG-WzCmbi0RpcHibX9r7jHAvzIZP2rJqtlib0GZEE89DQHvrzYmjogQ00TKfH27IA=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/9A7Trhxu4h22uRMIS_D0Sz828TsDwngNvDBYmMF1JA6WvmsF_MjQ3e-UMUpJSJymUgA=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/w6BdIJX3tHO-6jaPvkonXHMTso4m-lwathOKDP4yOK_x3J4TA4weF9AT9Gn0qwJI3A=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/QJahsvxoldjQ1pjJpYwSQH5UPIp0AWEJG6u7v514am9ykKnlGzCMH-qZG0VHZZlJr47c=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/5_lcn2bkn6RM1WUrJy5vevdZhgEaR68sSuSqOoAzkWEhz9yZU6vHA_2Qb5O6PVZIqPM=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/8ehrDpE7qSr0IavUVadqY6wLNDqGL4neT72AoVHkiLu3bY7KqkGAs-ZGFPJ9wW8uCg=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/R_VPaqzdCHb1cJqmQ1WM7faSFKCHlPrKNmHDRcYSfi-X_N2_pwJVLlhAjscinBcgIQ=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.goog