(10390, 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/r9xL_EBtLquqQVS22xXTKLvDVD-Mik18co9OiRoxyIP519Ywtjy8mLKW78g_h5OSLw=s180-rw', 'Mr Love: Queen\'s Choice', 'Elex', 'Role Playing', 'Who will be your soul mate? Mr Love: Queen\'s Choice is a romance simulation game that gives you the opportunity to text, chat and even call the main characters while developing your own career as a media producer.\n\nIn a world filled with superpowers, fantasy, and surprise, you will experience a girl‚Äôs whole life and get deeply involved with 4 male characters, feeling their romance, love, mystery and conflict in a deep story spanning dozens of episodes.\n\nVoice Acting\nDeepen your connection with your love interest by hearing his voice in English or Japanese. What type of voice do you prefer from a guy? Will it be soft, husky, lazy, sexy, pure, or deep? Mr. Love provides an immersive romance experience by allowing you to hear your love interest‚Äôs voice on your phone.\n\nJapanese and English languages can be switched at your command, with famous voice actors providing voices in Japanese. The cast includes popular anime voice actors, including Daisuke Hirakawa (Free! - Iwatobi Swim Club, Rei Ryugazaki), Tomokazu Sugita (Gintama, Gintoki Sakata), Y≈´ki Ono (Kuroko\'s Basketball, Taiga Kagami), and Tetsuya Kakihara (Fairy Tail, Natsu Dragneel).\n\nHigh-quality Graphics\nWant to watch the starry sky with him? Concentrate on work with him? See his genuine smile after saving a homeless dog? Ultra HD pictures, hundreds of delicate drawings, and CG will keep a record of every unforgettable moment between you and him.\n\nIntriguing Storyline\nThe world of Mr Love is full of mysterious superpowers. Here you will experience a unique combination of fantasy and romance. As the story unfolds, you will unravel the mysterious secrets about his and your own identities through dozens of episodes, a deep plot, and a passionate romance simulation.\n\nMessage Call and Connect\nKeep in touch with your love interest through messages, calls and social media. Chat with him via messenger and calls, and be the first one to comment on his online posts. You can even share your own moments and @ him.\n\nRun Your Company\nRun your own production studio! You will need to hire employees, produce TV programs (drama, episodes, interviews and more), keep an eye on each detail, and deal with emergencies. Make your own company succeed!\n\nGenius scientist, resolute agent, demanding CEO, and popular superstar. You seem to know him pretty well. But‚Ä¶do you actually know the real him?', 4.3, 34905, '0000-00-00', 1000000, '[\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/-ut8yIxi_EwPD9iVENOOodUKUe85JZ5ZeuSKlMqsSXv2BinXnQxj6gqi1MsSdqwmS5h4=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/iGaLp1xSznEnpcOspay4hARbgdlnSblu0yIke9Qa1HvnpnHYvyPBrCuvF7bXHzmU7n12=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/TqDo0DNfpAhfueTQ4Xas8xfTTt8sy-K-pKHkPcy7m2iJKrQC7ZZKPLORpJ2vcUUzoyU=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/AApzzynxQ6hx5kGgJH6rDEnxHN8yHtHSjBhIQqNXhTR-w-YUwM-RPDySBKUokd91UQ=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/EvdKHkcvIRgPCWqNOaplsRXyosJA8GSgefxB2QAGpj-XbsK7RohyhHmqiSamRbjCtIYm=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/r_x_C4T0zYDk7J1PRcqOdVauoKgXjSK5-QlsBkQ9zx2p9lYp9NlwyErSrJIov3m1JrE=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/_rpFkP_wtLBpM7o0Tv7TXC6jHUMtkLhC65PaRExoYWdnyfGO0HOSLRR5EfwAUwoIZwU=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/UmDhr361jhZtaexiCDtOcHuTkCPaCBANgIXY191XrPJ54QxYUwgy1c8YBcIv3G9Wy7Y=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/bC6a6udrZCylWhQBWitB1weDTxFBEdTsp9JvpYDaOSoCnLFgdFFhIxRiVg88AvKbI8o=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/DdBcAQXOQvebeQTx9MvNDutAk5_QWz1s6k4Jk6_gGaibe1ZAINclkbFRii8AgD2sDuY=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/cmzWGuxlBvejOnO8GVZqKLw1oEPc7IoxyaPWJMtn8h7mjnSSH6sYFGtEbcji40FMBfI=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.google