(10392, 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/5PKi2_nijs9zc4aqO-wreBK82PrT8CmuB7v5q_YlwQXqcCbtJQUw3k64u9RJ9a4Bfy2_=s180-rw', 'Pechka - Visual Novel, Story Game, Adventure Game', 'MazM (Story Games, Interactive Drama) Adventure', 'Adventure', 'In the early 20th century, people of a lost nation begin a fight for their country.\nThe journey of ‚ÄúPyotr,‚Äù for whom no nation could be his home.\n\nBecome the protagonist in a story based on real historical events!\nExperience the heartbreaking story firsthand through the tragic history of the war.\n\nüìñVisual Novel, Historical Story Game, War Story Game, Interactive Story\nPechka is MazM\'s 5th story game. This game takes place in Far East of Russia set in the early 20th century. Based on a true historical event, this historical visual novel is an interactive adventure game immersing the user into the story of the war.\n\n\nüéÆGame Features\n‚Ä¢ Visual novel style story game\n‚Ä¢ Story adventure game based on a true historical event\n‚Ä¢ Episodes are published weekly as a series system\n‚Ä¢ Experience the story of the war taking place in the Far East of Russia through this Text Game.\n‚Ä¢ Heartbreaking story game about the tragic history of the war\n‚Ä¢ Drama game with story line like that of a movie\n‚Ä¢ Multiple endings to the game depending on your choice\n\n\nüéñÔ∏è Play points about Pechka\n‚ñ∂ An interactive story game with a movie-like feel\n‚Ä¢ In ‚ÄúPechka‚Äù you can follow the captivating plot by exploring the map.\n‚Ä¢ Experience an epic tale based in the Russian Far East, in this unique dramatic production from MazM.\n\n‚ñ∂The chaotic Russian Far East in the early 20th century\n‚Ä¢ The game is set in Russian cities of the early 20th century.\n‚Ä¢ Explore Russian streets of the time and meet intriguing characters.\n‚Ä¢ You\'ll be able to spot some real historical figures in game.\n\n\n‚ñ∂Discover historical trivia that you can only find with MazM\n‚Ä¢ ‚ÄúPechka‚Äù is steeped in fascinating history.\n‚Ä¢ Collect historical ‚Äúfootnotes‚Äù while making your way through the story.\n‚Ä¢ Learn about the historical events that led to the Russian Far East descending into chaos.\n\n\nVisual Novel, Story Game, Adventure Game, Text Game, suited for those who love historical games.\nDrama directed by MazM, we bring you a heartbreaking and touching story.\nThose who are looking for a more special visual novel story game won\'t be disappointed.\n\n\nü§îAbout MazM\n‚Ä¢ MazM is a studio developing superb Story Game, Adventure Game, and Text Games. With dedication, we want to take praiseworthy stories and reinterpret them into games.\n‚Ä¢ We wish to instill a lasting impression in our players, like that which is made after experiencing a great book, movie or musical.\n‚Ä¢ Try various games such as Visual Novel, Story Game, Text Game, and Adventure Games through the indie game studio MazM.\n‚Ä¢ We, MazM, promise to deliver more touching Visual Novel, Adventure Game, and Indie Games.\n\nREAD_PHONE_STATE permission:\nThis permission is used to create an ID to identify a unique user within the game.\nSince this ID is used one-way encryption, the user\'s unique device information is unknown.', 4.2, 4828, '0000-00-00', 100000, '[\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/CrR-v3SqFw395fmk1zNWPQURbDOsgbNSB8rFg5WyfXeSo7JQorW5ce174POzbjRCbfI=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/br5Oh76GRrAgo5Fwt00JgNLz-yFEqTmlTnryqeQ0jSrQOgiscQq4mwrzodf1J1kTxg=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/e6IVr-URpNza2C-AQYDpIw48LY06Ds71qnq3ts7O7ZbFyo7Vo4ipOOa9UcqymYOivK0=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/1VQph_vgzjC-y4tznn3y6L8yxTm0SaNWbM4M3c5s0obWMfPbD8V20evnzO_W1WUmWw=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/urX9etapqC5Y5f0VGUkPT1k_pUCQ3SSu23OlTwfcgytt13u-g0LGIzRm9ISerBVY25XC=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/8X7xMQe5K8G43WjBrH2pFmH4v0BtlQi7GHEKLKP0E5GquQb7ZvqSrhFGc9swL-msbDA=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleuserc