(10393, 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/uNE-pgIMRKegfSEQ40KAMtnMfNRISgFmZGa7Ukcd_blcwB2Hmu6ZbfYGfgC0m981aQ=s180-rw', 'Coronation Street: Words & Design', 'Qiiwi Games AB', 'Word', 'Welcome to Coronation Street! It‚Äôs time for you to step onto the cobbles and help Ken Barlow, Bet Lynch and many of your favorite characters in this new crossword game, based on the popular drama, Coronation Street!\n\nHelp Ken give his old house a whole new look. Design it, decorate it and unearth buried treasures from Ken‚Äôs past.\n\nHead to the Rovers Return Inn where you can help Bet renovate the world famous pub and restore it to its former glory after it‚Äôs consumed by yet another fire. Decide on the legendary pub‚Äôs new look, and get it up and running again so Bet can serve the thirsty locals.\n\nIn order to progress in the game you will need to solve entertaining and funny crossword puzzles. Beat and complete these crossword levels to unlock new chapters in the story. Discover secrets and the hidden mysteries of Coronation Street with some classic characters.\n\nThe game features all sorts of shenanigans:\n‚Ä¢ A new type of word game: Solve word puzzles to progress in the story!\n‚Ä¢ Interior design: Create your dream Coronation Street look and make those legendary sets your own.\n‚Ä¢ Exciting crosswords: This game really needs a true word puzzle master. Could that be you?\n‚Ä¢ Famous characters: Meet Ken Barlow, Bet Lynch and many more Coronation Street legends as you progress through the game!\n‚Ä¢ Discover secrets and mysteries: Discover and unlock new rooms and hidden areas in Coronation Street!\n‚Ä¢ Collect and find famous Coronation Street items as you design and build Ken‚Äôs new Memorabilia Room - the Kenorabilia Room!\n\nIt‚Äôs time to show off your decorating skills as you choose from a wide range of styles and design Ken‚Äôs house, the Rovers Return Inn and many more. By being in control of all of the design decisions, you‚Äôll get to pick and choose many of the new items that go into the rooms, ensuring you have the final say on where Ken and Bet call home.\n\nOnce you‚Äôve solved your first Coronation Street crossword puzzle, you‚Äôre on your way to helping Ken and Bet solve their problems while creating your very own dream Coronation Street look!\nSo what are you waiting for? Download the Coronation Street Game, it‚Äôs flamin‚Äô belting!\n\nLearn more about the game on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Coronation-Street-Words-Design-121988852736512/\n\nQuestions? Contact our support team by sending an email to support@qiiwi.com', 4.2, 10676, '0000-00-00', 100000, '[\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/T3Y-L_exRCx7Q-jG7R3L3zBtXvG70l3OP1-BhB6fRbVJNIj75mMZnvkitlzUHw8BOYoJ=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/yL8m6GXC247QLjLjFx8hf4dAyoK5zJ_bl1NfyzUa5BkrN8UvkIQhFtcVzQfnZh5nfbD2=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/43VKjHxWxCk1_K2OTBCzAbVakVWthxhRS8_ouULHhNSsUnYMLCPQNBvOa31KHcgLxS4=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/cYNf3oZNhJyJIiNLVrfTCAr_qCg0q28dikUXC8zXkCsdPdHYnEkhZQeU_iFGEogBmd4=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/zmaZAiQDqDlAFet1HeburX3Z_7jszSsTKYyzqJEjBQ2_9Fmzvu-7VHO4hMK7ldXOggA=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/Os6yWGhjhpgDNTYPaJLTQP2Apqczh60tbfuezz0bWJWe3n5AIh53d0aeH6NpF0TLn9A=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/PNQsFNfCb3ICOqsTV1zhOgGLU_FJZK6cAAO9TQcV2_HypQJXy_hfhxwh8CifAPcHMg=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/LKzEAGYd6Av7gg4Wd3uj1hdxXiCoWKUNZxONnmzV_VVoWYQWztxFC5h4BZAhl3GvlA=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/V5cZuEh9x5ljwXSSqu_2gpcN2y7bue-72_vwdFtcM2NImfb2R0qMjcJCaJuPpYx-dKI=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/z9_11sIDKwMNw6Rb-fFN5BN71q7LyoU8J5_5p2Oy2H4q-1iuyd0hPTpzyURP8OicLsA=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/MLNSgXb2sH7ec9U62CtWPlFlAd3wkBbL8PhKs1DRACKRW5JO7fm7VZE9YQC9hfTxq9Q=w720-h310-rw\", \"https://pl